1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:55,744 --> 00:00:58,208
(Wu Shu)

4
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:00,460
Hello?

5
00:01:01,119 --> 00:01:01,869
Xuan.

6
00:01:02,368 --> 00:01:04,120
I'm at your company.

7
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:05,560
Where are you?

8
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,040
What's wrong? Why are you crying?

9
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:17,719
Want to have a drink?

10
00:01:27,648 --> 00:01:29,079
What's going on?

11
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:35,200
I went to your place,

12
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,799
but couldn't find you.

13
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:39,239
My phone died,

14
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,159
so I went to your company.

15
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:44,040
But that security guard
wouldn't let me in.

16
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:46,680
I borrowed a power bank there.

17
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:48,879
I just got my phone charged,

18
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,319
and your call came in.

19
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:52,439
Babe, it's a day off today.

20
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:54,040
Of course, they wouldn't let you in.

21
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,120
Why were you crying?

22
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:58,959
Who upset you?

23
00:02:00,879 --> 00:02:03,000
I went to celebrate that guy's birthday.

24
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:06,272
Didn't expect him and his ex
to get back together.

25
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:09,400
I even took a sweet couple photo
for them.

26
00:02:09,719 --> 00:02:12,479
I was just a joke.

27
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,599
Who is that guy?

28
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:16,520
What?

29
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,639
He made you cry,
and I'll make him bleed.

30
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,280
It's not his fault.

31
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:26,960
He's just not that into me.

32
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:32,199
Drinking? I'm in.

33
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:33,919
Just the two of you isn't fun.

34
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,000
Let's drink together.

35
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,080
To the four of us,

36
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,759
may we find good partners.

37
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:45,960
Drink...

38
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:46,599
Me.

39
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:50,840
Good boss.

40
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,439
- Wait, I...
- Drink till we drop!

41
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,000
Cheers!

42
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,319
Drink up.

43
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,680
What are you looking at?

44
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:41,800
Xuan, stop hugging him.

45
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,400
Drink up.

46
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,639
Liao Bei, can you take Wu Shu home?

47
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,300
Sure.

48
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,159
I'm not drunk.

49
00:04:02,599 --> 00:04:03,439
Where are my legs?

50
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,120
Where are my legs?

51
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:07,520
Why can't I find my legs?

52
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,504
I'll take you home.

53
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:43,199
You're not drinking anymore?

54
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:44,740
Leaving.

55
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,800
Let's go home.

56
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:58,779
Let's go.

57
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:08,160
Put me down.

58
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,519
Why did you have to carry me back?

59
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,480
I don't want you to envy others.

60
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,920
I-I didn't.

61
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,959
Put me down.

62
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:17,459
Stop that.

63
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:22,920
I really didn't.

64
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:25,519
I saw Liao Bei was drunk too,

65
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:28,240
and was worried
if he could get Wu Shu home safely.

66
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,120
Don't worry.

67
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:31,929
He may talk mean,

68
00:05:32,224 --> 00:05:33,439
but he's quite reliable.

69
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:36,920
You're such a jealousy monster.

70
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:39,319
I just don't want you to envy others.

71
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:44,399
Did you know about
Liao Bei sponsoring me before?

72
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:47,399
I only knew he had
a really unlucky streak for a while.

73
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,639
So I suggested he do some good deeds

74
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:50,959
to build up some good karma.

75
00:05:52,639 --> 00:05:53,279
What about you?

76
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,120
What good deeds have you done?

77
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,879
I'm naturally perfect.

78
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:57,920
Don't need that.

79
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,360
Xuan.

80
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,279
Look at the moon tonight.

81
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:10,959
It's beautiful.

82
00:06:27,259 --> 00:06:29,920
♪I saw my love, my love♪

83
00:06:30,107 --> 00:06:31,776
♪Meet you♪

84
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:35,600
Qiu Lin, turn on the high beams.

85
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:36,379
Yes.

86
00:06:36,411 --> 00:06:38,400
♪Lonely, lonely, in my life♪

87
00:06:38,912 --> 00:06:41,344
♪Calling, where are you♪

88
00:06:41,947 --> 00:06:45,472
♪I wish I could kiss on you♪

89
00:06:46,459 --> 00:06:48,693
♪I'll wait for you♪

90
00:06:49,307 --> 00:06:52,079
♪Something lost in my soul♪

91
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:52,680
Follow her.

92
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,160
Take her home.

93
00:06:55,515 --> 00:07:00,160
♪Love, love, I fell in love, are you♪

94
00:07:02,811 --> 00:07:07,584
♪Love, I see the sky. It's you♪

95
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:10,144
Tell me about your past.

96
00:07:12,279 --> 00:07:14,720
It's all unhappy memories.

97
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:16,040
Except...

98
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,720
Except what?

99
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:19,920
Nothing.

100
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:27,040
Has your grandpa always
treated you and your brother bad?

101
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:30,639
He was good to my brother,
just not to me.

102
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,960
Sometimes, for somehow,

103
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,079
he'd hit me.

104
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,560
My brother tried to reason.

105
00:07:36,439 --> 00:07:38,959
But that would only
make him hit me harder.

106
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:42,480
Ji Xuan, can you imagine?

107
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:46,240
I had an unhappy childhood
in the Song family.

108
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,240
What about your parents?

109
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,000
I never met my mother.

110
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:55,439
My father passed away when I was six.

111
00:07:57,360 --> 00:08:00,160
You've been living a hard time
all these years.

112
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:14,480
Ji Xuan.

113
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:18,160
Last time you asked about
the meaning of this ring.

114
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:21,319
I really miss my brother.

115
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:54,600
Today,

116
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,720
only one of you two can go.

117
00:08:59,456 --> 00:09:00,799
Decide for yourselves.

118
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:18,860
Brother.

119
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:22,240
You wouldn't kill me
while I'm asleep, would you?

120
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:24,919
No.

121
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:26,519
Neither would I.

122
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,480
We're brothers.

123
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,519
We live together.

124
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:30,960
We die together.

125
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,840
Don't worry.

126
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,000
Hey!

127
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:48,879
The floor is cold.

128
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,519
I want to put a coat on you.

129
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:01,879
Do you know your biggest problem?

130
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,600
Too soft-hearted.

131
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:10,360
Grandpa doesn't like
soft-hearted people.

132
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:13,480
To survive, you need
to learn to be ruthless.

133
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:38,639
No.

134
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,000
Zhaoli.

135
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,559
Brother.

136
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:42,960
No.

137
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:44,720
Brother.

138
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,159
Brother.

139
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,639
Brother.

140
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,720
No!

141
00:11:11,392 --> 00:11:13,184
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

142
00:11:13,344 --> 00:11:15,224
♪Flickering neon lights♪

143
00:11:15,424 --> 00:11:18,752
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

144
00:11:19,264 --> 00:11:21,536
♪Every star is♪

145
00:11:21,824 --> 00:11:25,696
♪My heartbeat for you♪

146
00:11:27,008 --> 00:11:28,832
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

147
00:11:28,992 --> 00:11:30,544
♪And land in your arms♪

148
00:11:30,944 --> 00:11:34,400
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

149
00:11:34,656 --> 00:11:37,216
♪In the blue sky♪

150
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:41,408
♪Your smile still lingers♪

151
00:11:42,336 --> 00:11:45,984
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

152
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:49,904
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

153
00:11:50,112 --> 00:11:53,024
♪Can't find a cure♪

154
00:11:53,024 --> 00:11:57,536
♪To love you after we've parted♪

155
00:11:57,728 --> 00:12:01,760
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

156
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:05,624
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

157
00:12:05,624 --> 00:12:07,424
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

158
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:12,672
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

159
00:12:13,312 --> 00:12:17,024
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

160
00:12:17,216 --> 00:12:19,968
♪Can't find a cure♪

161
00:12:20,096 --> 00:12:24,736
♪To love you after we've parted♪

162
00:12:24,904 --> 00:12:28,672
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

163
00:12:28,896 --> 00:12:32,480
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

164
00:12:32,704 --> 00:12:34,744
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

165
00:12:34,744 --> 00:12:39,744
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
